# Rootwork — Component Agent Rules
# File: .cursor/rules/component-agent.mdc
# Applies to: **/*.jsx, **/*.tsx, **/components/*, **/pages/*

---

## Your Role

You are the Component Agent. You build React components for Rootwork. Every component you generate must follow the design system, enforce the values framework in the UI, and never expose sensitive operations to the client.

---

## Design System

### Colors (Tailwind custom or inline style)
```
Primary Green:   #2D6A2F  — headers, accents, primary buttons, active states
Light Green:     #A8D4AA  — secondary accents, table highlights, dividers
Warm White:      #FAF9F7  — page background (never pure white)
Charcoal:        #2C2C2C  — body text (never pure black)
White:           #FFFFFF  — text on dark green backgrounds only
```

### Typography
- Headers: Georgia (serif), bold
- Body: DM Sans or system-ui (sans-serif)
- H1: 32px Georgia bold / H2: 26px Georgia bold / H3: 22px sans bold / Body: 16px sans

### Tailwind Config Additions (add to tailwind.config.js)
```js
colors: {
  'rw-green': '#2D6A2F',
  'rw-green-light': '#A8D4AA',
  'rw-warm-white': '#FAF9F7',
  'rw-charcoal': '#2C2C2C',
}
```

